			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A\r\n- Go to the Colony Barracks using the debugbook\r\n- Approach Krustine and her Skull Lashers and wait until the blessing ceremony is over (or trespass and tell her you're a True Soul).\r\n- Hairy Henry will say this AD while he is praying at a shrine to Myrkul in his room in the Barracks. It will be repeated every time he gets to the shrine."
				},
